;;
;; Given the following facts (obtaine via NLP)
;;
;; “I’m Bob.   I live in China.   I like chicken feet.”
;; “I’m Jane.   I live in France.   I like pizza.”
;; “I’m Jack.   I live in China.   I like chicken feet.”
;; ‘I’m Jim.  I live in China.”
